tsc --init       >>>>>>>>>    used to create simple ts config file

npm init -y   >>>>>>>>   used to create package.json file

to save all output files in /dist folder   >>>>>>> go to tsconfig.json and change >>>> "outDir": "./dist",   

tsc -w    >>>>   to run in waatch mode , used to create output files in /dist folder

to run our file  -------->     "test": "echo \"Error: no test specified\" && exit 1"      >>> to >>>     "start": "lite-server" 
then npm start to run our application
